						<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">World War II</span></h1>
						<div id="bodyContent">
								<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-navigation">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">"WWII" redirects here. For other uses, see <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WWII_(disambiguation)" title="WWII (disambiguation)">WWII (disambiguation)</a>.  For Winston Churchill's history, see <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Second_World_War_(book_series)" title="The Second World War (book series)">The Second World War (book series)</a>.</div>
