Over 45,000,000<br />
<b>Total dead:</b><br />
Over 61,000,000 <small>(1937–45)</small><br />
<small><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_War_II_casualties" title="World War II casualties">...<i>further details</i></a></small></td>
