<ul>
<li class="nv-view"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Template:TopicTOC-World_War_II" title="Template:TopicTOC-World War II"><span title="View this template" style="">v</span></a></li>
<li class="nv-talk"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Template_talk:TopicTOC-World_War_II" title="Template talk:TopicTOC-World War II"><span title="Discuss this template" style="">t</span></a></li>
<li class="nv-edit"><a class="external text" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:TopicTOC-World_War_II&amp;action=edit"><span title="Edit this template" style="">e</span></a></li>
