<li id="cite_note-Schoenherr-386"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Schoenherr_386-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Schoenherr_386-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web">Schoenherr, Steven (2007). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://web.archive.org/web/20080509054959/http://history.sandiego.edu/gen/WW2Timeline/espionage.html">"Code Breaking in World War II"</a>. History Department at the University of San Diego. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://history.sandiego.edu/gen/WW2Timeline/espionage.html">the original</a> on 9 May 2008<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 15 November 2009</span>.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWorld+War+II&amp;rft.aufirst=Steven&amp;rft.aulast=Schoenherr&amp;rft.au=Schoenherr%2C+Steven&amp;rft.btitle=Code+Breaking+in+World+War+II&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fhistory.sandiego.edu%2Fgen%2FWW2Timeline%2Fespionage.html&amp;rft.pub=History+Department+at+the+University+of+San+Diego&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
